    • User

      public User(String name, String gender, String mobileNumber, LocalDate dateOfBirth, String address, String aboutMe, String email, String password, String profilePic, String myTodos, long userId, boolean isDeleted)
      Parameterized constructor for creating a User object.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the user.
      gender - The gender of the user.
      mobileNumber - The mobile number of the user.
      dateOfBirth - The date of birth of the user.
      address - The address of the user.
      aboutMe - A short description about the user.
      email - The email address of the user.
      password - The password of the user's account.
      profilePic - The profile picture of the user.
      myTodos - JSON representation of user's to-do list.
      userId - The user's unique identifier.
      isDeleted - Flag indicating if the user is deleted.
